Details: Cochin International Language Academy (CILA) is an international institution for English Language Training and Teacher Training. We create international opportunities for English Language teachers in Non-English Speaking regions such as Western Europe, Central / Eastern Europe, Asia, Latin America, Middle East / North Africa and Sub-Saharan Africa. We also provide English Language training to students who wish to study or work abroad particularly in an English speaking country. Cochin International Language Academy (Cila) is owned and managed by Js Training Solutions Private Limited, a company registered and incorporated under the Companies Act, 1956. CILA is located in Angamaly, near to the Cochin International airport. It is only 2 minutes drive to the Angamaly Railway station. The School is managed by native English speakers from the UK and Canada with multiple years of experience in teaching English. We provide variety of courses such as the Trinity Cert. TESOL for English Teachers to become a qualified English teacher to speakers of other languages, IELTS for those who wish to work or study abroad, Business English, Spoken English for Adults, Spoken English for Children and even 1 to 1 Skype sessions. Our teachers are well qualified and trained to teach English using the modern methods. Students enjoy learning English in our centre. Two of our teachers are former IELTS examiners and have worked in countries around the world such as the UK, Canada and in the Middle East. So you can be confident that your learning is 100% correct. So, CILA becomes your first choice to learn and teach the English Language. Contact us for more details.

Details: Competition is an indispensable part of life. To achieve success and sustain it, a strategic approach towards competence and methodology is important. It is here that Talent plays a frontal role. Sometimes it is born talent; in other cases it is acquired and success is achieved once that talent is developed. Talent Sindia was devised with one such motto. It is in the firm belief in the dictum that Everyone is talented and talent can blossom only if it is nurtured properly. Thus the mission statement of Talent Sindia is We Nurture Talent. Founded in 1999 by Shri.C.Nandakumar, an alumnus of IT-BHU, the institute has been focusing on training and coaching students towards the Joint Entrance Examination (Main){ called JEE Main  erstwhile AIEEE.} for admissions to the NITs and the Joint Entrance Examination (Advanced){ called JEE ADV.} for admissions to the IITs. The institute is located at Vytilla, in Ernakulam, Kochi. (Kerala)The institute provides coaching for Engineering entrance exams like IIT- JEE (JEE ADV) and JEE-MAIN to students of classes X, XI and XII. The class room programmes are interactive and promotes different techniques of problem solving. This enables students to develop conceptual clarity, rather than rote learning.
